lead_paragraph: Tigers outfielder Tyler Collins will not be suspended by Major League Baseball for directing an obscene gesture at booing home fans in Detroit after losing a ball in the lights Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Collins Won't Face Suspension From MLB Over Gesture at Fans
